description: Recall FastAPI backend conventions
globs: apps/api/**/*.py
alwaysApply: false
---

# Recall API (Python)

- async/await for all IO; full type hints; Pydantic v2 schemas
- Config via `app/core/config.py` — never read `os.environ` elsewhere
- Background jobs: wrap body in try/except; never raise into chat path
- Mock LiteLLM, Redis, Google, Neon in tests — zero real network calls
- Format/lint: `uv run ruff format . && uv run ruff check .`
- Coverage target 80%+ (`pytest --cov=app --cov-fail-under=80`)
